        <li><strong>Query association:</strong> First businesses mentioned become associated with query types</li>
        <li><strong>Ecosystem positions:</strong> Early platform presence secures better positioning</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Defensive Strategies</h3>
      <p>Protecting existing market position requires proactive AI visibility work:</p>
      <ul>
